{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Noun===
'''April fool'''
# [[Practical joke]] played on 1st April, [[April Fools' Day]]
# Person subjected to the practical joke on 1st April.
#: Any one imposed on, or sent on a bootless errand, on the first of April; which day it is the custom among the lower people, children, and servants, by dropping empty papers carefully doubled up, sending persons on absurd messages, and such like contrivances, to impose on every one they can, and then to salute them with the title of April Fool.

